    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tesserarii is a dice rolling, rogue-like strategy game all about increasing the power of your dice and winning big.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176790/extras/39158503039170adf94c1119bd44a6cd.poster.avif?t=1765449245\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176790/extras/39158503039170adf94c1119bd44a6cd.webm?t=1765449245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176790/extras/39158503039170adf94c1119bd44a6cd.mp4?t=1765449245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the satisfying nature of Tesserarii as you watch your strategic choices roll out in front of you.  You'll need your wits about you at every turn to ensure your best chance of defeating powerful bosses, or leave your fate up to lady luck and risk it all.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176790/extras/e9641863e35057a7ebfd4d0aa5fb6131.poster.avif?t=1765449245\" width=800 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176790/extras/e9641863e35057a7ebfd4d0aa5fb6131.webm?t=1765449245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176790/extras/e9641863e35057a7ebfd4d0aa5fb6131.mp4?t=1765449245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't let your guard down though! Each battle requires you to best deal with the randomness of rolling dice.  Break the game through combining different powerups and elements at the right time to ignite your dice and progress through the stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176790/extras/f562cbdc8c72ba5fc4c5d2cb064cb197.poster.avif?t=1765449245\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176790/extras/f562cbdc8c72ba5fc4c5d2cb064cb197.webm?t=1765449245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176790/extras/f562cbdc8c72ba5fc4c5d2cb064cb197.mp4?t=1765449245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over <strong>130+ powerups</strong> (with more coming soon).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5</strong> <strong>characters</strong> to unlock with unique starting stats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8</strong> <strong>elemental powers</strong> for your dice to unlock through runs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Powerups to modify <strong>17 different stats</strong> to best suit your build.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over <strong>50 enemy types</strong> to encounter and defeat<strong>. </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Infinite ways to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
